<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Dear <%= @booking.nurse.name %></h2>
    <p>
      I am please that you have picked the booking.
      The following is the booking details. 
    </p>
  
    <br><br>
    <p><strong>Time:</strong>     <%= @booking.order_datetime.strftime("%l %p %d/%m/%Y") %> for <%= @booking.hours %> hours</p>
    <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= @booking.hospital %> <%= @booking.location %></p>
    <p><strong>Nurse:</strong>    <%= @booking.nurse.name %></p>
    <p><strong>Income:</strong>   <%= number_to_currency(@booking.cost, precision: 0)  %> </p>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong>  <%= @booking.contact_person %></p>
    <p><Strong>Phone No.:</Strong> <%= @booking.contact_phone_no %> </p>
    <p><strong>Status:</strong>   <%= @booking.status %></p>
    <p><strong>Payment:</strong>  <%= @booking.payment %></p>
    <br><br>

    <p>
      Please be patient and wait for the client's confirmation.  Should you have any questions regarding to 
      the mentioned order, feel free to contact us.</p>  
    <br><br>
    <p>
      Thanks for working with us and have a happy order! </p>
    <br><br>
    <p>Regards</p>
    <p>Partner Service</p>
    <p>Lets Nurse</p>
  </body>
</html>
